{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"451001c0a5","title":"给司徒美堂的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0730a39abd","index":0,"year":1945,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"451001c0a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"5d75da6670","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东修改件刊印。"},{"id":"cc48985019","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":5,"text":"司徒美堂（一八六八——一九五五），广东开平人，当时任致公党美洲总部主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3195e6cbc6","type":"title","text":"给司徒美堂的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5"},{"id":"cc48985019","type":"appellation","text":"纽约司徒美堂先生勋鉴：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5"},{"id":"dfb64b365d","type":"paragraph","text":"顷接十一月二十七日代电，反对内战，力争民主，不胜钦佩。敝党代表团久已抵渝出席即将召开之政治协商会议，并已向政府当局提议立即无条件全面停止内战，结束一党专政，成立民主联合政府，以谋国家之团结、统一与和平建设。尚祈贵党与全美侨胞，一致主张，促其实现。民族前途，实深利赖。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5"},{"id":"1dd7d58767","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席 毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5"},{"id":"0d2e8bcc52","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5"}],"page":{"id":"916b38d91e","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"451001c0a5","start":99,"end":99}}}},"__N_SSG":true}